{"title":"海情篇","authors":["苗得雨"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":9,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海情篇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗得雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逐浪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪在一阵阵笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪在一阵阵跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逗着一个拣海的老者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前追呀后追，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左转呀右绕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转着绕着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把拣忘了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着退去的浪跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着上来的浪跳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"篮子丢了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已拣到的青的绿的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又随浪去了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸上人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"见一个孩子在跳跃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原来老者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把失去的又拣到了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海滩上的情侣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一下子都成了顽皮蛋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃上晒了一天的沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在跳呀蹦，在转呀旋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把脚插进沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把手伸向沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把脸贴向沙滩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把心埋进沙滩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱掺上沙子就更纯了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暖洋洋里滚滚翻翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青年变成孩子就更可爱了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有多少天真跌进热恋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪，在脚下滚来滚去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选镜头，要选在这时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人，在浪上跳来跳去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看勇气，要看在这时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活，在浪中穿来穿去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时光，美丽在这时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"视线，被浪打来打去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想，收获在这时。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}